bolism oncology musculoskeletal system paediatrics pain management and respiratory system and consumer health products such as dermocosmetics sunscreens food supplements antilice products insect repellants overthecounter medicines and infant nutrition products the company also provides personalized medicines generic drugs ingredients excipients intermediates food ingredients flavorings sweeteners animal nutrition and nutraceuticals and vaccines solutions for allergies grupo ferrer internacional sa was formerly known as laboratorios ferrer sl and changed its name to grupo ferrer internacional sa in  the company was founded in  and is based in barcelona spain with pharmaceutical production plants in barcelona and murcia spain and a logistics center in girona spain detailed description av diagonal ª plantabarcelona  spainfounded in  phone      fax      wwwferrercom key executives for grupo ferrer internacional sa jordi ramentol chief executive officer joan fanés chief financial officer mario rovirosa chief operating pharma antoni villaró vice president of corporate strategy fernando garcia alonso chief scientific officer compensation as of fiscal year  grupo ferrer internacional sa key developments albany molecular research inc announces agreement with ferrer and accord healthcare to jointly develop manufacture and commercialize parenteral drug products feb   albany molecular research inc announced that it has entered into an agreement with the pharmaceutical group ferrer  and accord healthcare inc to jointly develop and manufacture an undisclosed complex parenteral drug product for registration and subsequent commercialization in the united states with the option to partner on additional drug products under terms of the agreement amri will work with ferrer to develop and initially provide cgmp manufacturing and analytical support for the registration of the new product accord healthcare will be responsible for advancing the product candidate through regulatory submission and commercialization ferrer to open cardiovascular facility in mexico to produce cardiovascular polypills sep   ferrer has announced plans to open a cardiovascular facility in mexico focusing on the production of cardiovascular polypills antihypertensive statin and aspirin reports news agency notimex ferrer aims to produce these cardiovascular polypills for the public sector in mexico which will lead to the launch of a production facility in mexico to supply the us and latin american markets cardiovascular polypills are an innovative research and development rd technology by ferrer for the secondary prevention of cardiovascular events in patients already in treatment ensuring the stability and noninteraction of its components the objective is to improve adherence and reduce the risk of further cardiovascular events this project is being undertaken with the spanish national centre for cardiovascular research cnic and the endorsement of the world heart federation similar private companies by industry company name region ability pharmaceuticals sl europe activery biotech sl europe aelix therapeutics sl europe albajuna therapeutics sl europe alcaliber sa europe recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region lawyers committee for civil rights under law united states nyc inc united states the advertising council inc united states bertelsmann ag europe rush university united states sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z 